      <odd id="aspace_6a7017f28a15aba616e7e05703f8f10e">
         <head>General note</head>
         <p>Forms part of Yale Record Group 10-A (YRG 10-A), Records of Yale College classes.</p>  
      </odd>
      <acqinfo id="aspace_2e1019ca9b60126aab81eb063fa3a887">
         <head>Immediate Source of Acquisition</head>
         <p>The records were transferred from the Association of Yale Alumni (AYA), 1993.</p>  
      </acqinfo>
      <accessrestrict id="aspace_3e054d047a2124317985ab556e6f8200">
         <head>Conditions Governing Access</head>
         <p>Access to the records is partially restricted. See Collection Contents for details.</p>
         <p>Original born digital files, as well as preservation masters, may not be accessed due to their fragility. Researchers must consult use copies, or if none exist request that they be made. Born digital files cannot be accessed remotely. System requirements include a Manuscripts and Archives computer and file viewing software.</p>  
      </accessrestrict>
      <prefercite id="aspace_52ac6f6aa9b30b215114c4c076b73f11">
         <head>Preferred Citation</head>
         <p>Class of 1942, Yale College, Records (RU 27). Manuscripts and Archives, Yale University Library.</p>  
      </prefercite>
      <arrangement id="aspace_428d1d94619c33ab096b4d9f8b6a9004">
         <head>Arrangement</head>
         <p>The records are arranged by accession.</p>  
      </arrangement>
      <scopecontent id="aspace_ff6fda3c9deae18e9fd61f74f7e54a09">
         <head>Scope and Contents</head>
         <p>The records consist of class notes, correspondence, minutes, photographs, and other records concerning reunions, donations, meetings, and other activities of the Yale College Class of 1942.</p>  
      </scopecontent>
